<div class="container">

  <h3 class="mt-4">Your compatability with <a href="/{{friend._id}}">{{friend.name}}</a></h3>

  <div class="card-deck friends-deck compat-deck">
    <div class="card" style="width: 18rem;">
      <a href="/profile/{{req.user._id}}">
        <img class="card-img-top img-thumbnail" src="{{user.imgPath}}" alt="Card image cap">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h5 class="card-title text-center">{{user.username}}</h5>
          <p class="card-text text-center">
            <span>{{user.zodiac}}</span><br>
          </p>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>


  {{!-- here are the compatability icons --}}
  <div>
    {{#ifEquals compatability 1}}
    <i class="fas fa-skull-crossbones fa-8x"></i>
    {{else}}
    {{/ifEquals}}

    {{#ifEquals compatability 2}}
    <i class="fas fa-exclamation-triangle fa-8x"></i>
    {{else}}
    {{/ifEquals}}


    {{#ifEquals compatability 3}}
    <i class="fas fa-thumbs-up fa-8x"></i>
    {{else}}
    {{/ifEquals}}

    {{#ifEquals compatability 4}}
    <i class="fas fa-heart fa-8x"></i>
    {{else}}
    {{/ifEquals}}

    {{#ifEquals compatability 5}}
    <i class="fas fa-grin-hearts fa-8x"></i>
    {{else}}
    {{/ifEquals}}


  </div>

  <a href="/{{friend._id}}"></a>

  <div class="card" style="width: 18rem;">
    <img class="card-img-top img-thumbnail" src="{{friend.imgPath}}" alt="Card image cap">

    <div class="card-body">
      <h5 class="card-title text-center">{{friend.name}}</h5>
      <p class="card-text text-center">
        {{!-- <span>{{friend.birthday}}</span><br>
        <span>{{friend.birthtime}}</span><br>
        <span>{{friend.birthplace}}</span><br>
        <span>{{friend.location}}</span><br> --}}
        <span>{{friend.zodiac}}</span><br>
      </p>

    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<br>
<br>

<h3>Your compatability score is {{compatability}}/5.</h3>


<div class="card card-body compat-info">
  <span class="compatability">
    <h4><span class="zodiac-compat-h4">{{user.zodiac}}</span> & <span class="zodiac-compat-h4">{{friend.zodiac}}</span></h4>


    <br>
    <br>
    {{#ifEquals compatability 1}}
    This is a disasterous pairing. You have a hard time understanding each other, and are likely ill-prepared to read
    each other's reactions and moods. Miscommunication and frustration are likely down the road. Please proceed with
    caution.
    {{else}}
    {{/ifEquals}}

    {{#ifEquals compatability 2}}
    Hmmm this one can go either way. If you're willing to put in the effort to acquaint yourselves with each other's
    communication styles and idiosyncracies, you could find fulfillment in this relationship. But be wary â€” chances of
    hurt and misunderstanding are high. It can end in disaster just as easily as it could end in fulfillment.
    {{else}}
    {{/ifEquals}}

    {{#ifEquals compatability 3}}
    This is a solid match
    {{else}}
    {{/ifEquals}}

    {{#ifEquals compatability 4}}
    This is a strong match. There might be some hesitation toward getting to know each other at first, but don't let
    fear triumph over curiosity. You have the chance to nurture a strong connection that will be both fulfilling and
    joyous.
    {{else}}
    {{/ifEquals}}

    {{#ifEquals compatability 5}}
    Your star signs are as compatible as they come. You share a mutual understanding forged by complimentary energies.
    Whether your relationship is platonic, romantic, or otherwise, it will likely be a great source of fulfillment for
    both of you.
    {{else}}
    {{/ifEquals}}
  </span>
</div>

